Welcome to the U.S. court system! Before you go to court, you've got some preparation to do.
Evidence is very important in any case, as pretty much all of the case will be spent discussing your evidence. Before you start your case, you'll need [color=yellow]2 pieces[/color] of evidence.
Your first piece should show that the house was damaged, and your second should show that the insurance should cover the damage. Press the [color=red]red[/color] button when you're ready. Good luck!
=> END